cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.SI

The paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques for product recommendation and customer profiling in online retail, which falls under the category of machine learning and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques for customer segmentation, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of the proposed architecture to solve retail and distribution pain-points, which could fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
